WEBVTT

00:00:59.994 --> 00:01:01.589
And a lot of my school teachers

00:01:01.589 --> 00:01:04.717
didn't appreciate it much either.

00:01:04.717 --> 00:01:06.852
You see, since the age of about five

00:01:06.852 --> 00:01:10.525
I've always asked the question, but why?

00:01:10.525 --> 00:01:13.154
But why does the Earth go around the sun?

00:01:13.154 --> 00:01:14.991
But why is blood red?

00:01:14.991 --> 00:01:17.298
But why do I have to go to school?

00:01:17.298 --> 00:01:19.311
But why do I have to respect the teachers

00:01:19.311 --> 00:01:21.178
and authority?

00:01:21.178 --> 00:01:22.820
And little did I realize

00:01:22.820 --> 00:01:25.598
that this question would become the basis

00:01:25.598 --> 00:01:28.251
of everything I would do.

00:01:28.251 --> 00:01:30.006
And so it was